Package net.sf.jguiraffe.examples.tutorial.viewset

Class ColorListModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.jguiraffe.examples.tutorial.viewset.ColorListModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ListModel
    public class ColorListModel
extends Object
implements ListModel

    A ListModel implementation for combo boxes that allow the user to choose a color.

    This model contains all default colors. For the default colors there is an enumeration class in the ColorHelper class. The display names are resolved from resources; the name of the resource ID is derived from the name of the color.
